Thanks to CodeDraken for their helpful resource: https://dev.to/learn2dev/css-shorts-spoilers-and-hidden-content-3621

Uses js-cookies for cookie management: https://github.com/js-cookie/js-cookie

This is a mix of that and my own work to make it dynamic. Initially made for [Neokosmos](https://neokosmos.space), I am releasing this to public so more people can use it.
